{"type":"message","id":"418829c9","parentId":"802cc4ee","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:55:07.577Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_832e3e55695441439e42f85a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nmock_server.py — 企享云 API 模拟服务器（本地测试用）\n\n模拟所有企享云接口的返回，让你在不调真实税务局的情况下跑通整个流程。\n启动: python3 mock_server.py\n地址: http://localhost:18800\n\n测试时把 config.json 的 base_url 改成 http://localhost:18800 即可。\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport time\nimport random\nimport string\nfrom http.server import HTTPServer, BaseHTTPRequestHandler\n\n\ndef gen_task_id():\n    return str(random.randint(100000000000, 999999999999))\n\ndef gen_req_id():\n    return ''.join(random.choices(string.hexdigits.lower(), k=32))\n\n# 存储已发起的任务（task_id → 状态）\nTASKS = {}\n\n\nclass MockHandler(BaseHTTPRequestHandler):\n\n    def _read_body(self) -> dict:\n        length = int(self.headers.get(\"Content-Length\", 0))\n        if length:\n            return json.loads(self.rfile.read(length))\n        return {}\n\n    def _respond(self, data: dict, status=200):\n        body = json.dumps(data, ensure_ascii=False).encode()\n        self.send_response(status)\n        self.send_header(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json\")\n        self.send_header(\"Content-Length\", str(len(body)))\n        self.end_headers()\n        self.wfile.write(body)\n\n    def do_POST(self):\n        path = self.path.split(\"?\")[0]\n        body = self._read_body()\n        agg = body.get(\"aggOrgId\", \"mock_org\")\n\n        print(f\"[MOCK] POST {path}  body_keys={list(body.keys())}\")\n\n        # ── 鉴权 ────────────────────────\n        if path == \"/api-66569900\":\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"2000\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"token\": \"mock_token_for_testing\", \"expiresIn\": 1296000},\n            })\n\n        # ── 登录相关 ────────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-164618489\":  # check_quick_login\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"2000\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"canQuickLogin\": True},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-164576229\":  # login_tax_bureau\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"2000\", \"success\": True,\n                \"message\": \"登录成功\",\n            })\n\n        # ── 获取申报清册 ────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-66960663\":  # initiate_roster_entry\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"roster\"}  # 直接完成\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        # ── 初始化 ──────────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-69420373\":  # load_init_data_task\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"init\", \"yzpzzlDm\": body.get(\"yzpzzlDm\")}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-69497719\":  # get_init_data\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\n                    \"yzpzzlDm\": body.get(\"yzpzzlDm\", \"BDA0610606\"),\n                    \"period\": body.get(\"period\"),\n                    \"year\": body.get(\"year\"),\n                    \"initFields\": {\n                        \"sales_amount\": 0,\n                        \"output_tax\": 0,\n                        \"input_tax\": 0,\n                    },\n                    \"form_schema\": {\"fields\": [\"sales_amount\", \"exempt_sales\", \"tax_rate\"]},\n                },\n            })\n\n        # ── 上传申报 ───────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67298736\":  # upload_tax_report\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"declare\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        # ── 查询申报结果 ───────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67919304\":  # query_tax_report_result\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\n                    \"business_status\": 3,\n                    \"declareResult\": \"申报成功\",\n                    \"skje\": \"0.00\",\n                },\n            })\n\n        # ── 简易申报 ───────────────────\n        elif \"/loadSimplifiedDeclareTask\" in path:\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"simplified\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif \"/querySimplifiedDeclareTaskInfo\" in path:\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": 3, \"result\": \"申报成功\"},\n            })\n\n        # ── 财报 ───────────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67585521\":  # upload_financial_report\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"financial\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-67922325\":  # query_financial_report_result\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": 3, \"result\": \"财报申报成功\"},\n            })\n\n        # ── 轮询任务状态（核心） ────────\n        elif \"/queryTaskInfo\" in path:\n            tid = str(body.get(\"taskId\", \"\"))\n            task = TASKS.get(tid, {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"unknown\"})\n\n            result_data = {\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": task[\"status\"], \"taskId\": tid},\n            }\n\n            # 根据任务类型附加数据\n            if task[\"type\"] == \"roster\":\n                result_data[\"data\"][\"rosterEntries\"] = [\n                    {\n                        \"yzpzzlDm\": \"BDA0610606\",\n                        \"zsxmMc\": \"增值税及附加税费（小规模纳税人）\",\n                        \"tax_code\": \"VAT\",\n                        \"declareStatus\": \"未申报\",\n                        \"ssqQ\": \"2026-02-01\",\n                        \"ssqZ\": \"2026-02-28\",\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"yzpzzlDm\": \"BDA0610100\",\n                        \"zsxmMc\": \"企业所得税（季报）\",\n                        \"tax_code\": \"CIT\",\n                        \"declareStatus\": \"未申报\",\n                        \"ssqQ\": \"2026-01-01\",\n                        \"ssqZ\": \"2026-03-31\",\n                    },\n                ]\n\n            self._respond(result_data)\n\n        # ── PDF 下载 ──────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67645165\":  # load_pdf_task\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"pdf\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-212658227\":  # query_pdf_result\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\n                    \"business_status\": 3,\n                    \"pdfUrl\": \"https://mock.example.com/receipt.pdf\",\n                    \"structured_data\": {\n                        \"company_name\": \"模拟测试公司\",\n                        \"period\": \"2026-02\",\n                        \"total_tax\": \"0.00\",\n                        \"status\": \"申报成功\",\n                    },\n                },\n            })\n\n        # ── 缴款 ─────────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67662292\":  # load_payment_task\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"payment\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-67976986\":  # query_payment_result\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": 3, \"result\": \"缴款成功\"},\n            })\n\n        # ── 申报信息查询 ──────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-66965100\":  # load_declare_info_task\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"info\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        # ── 漏报检查 ─────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-66968884\":\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"missing_check\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid, \"hasMissing\": False},\n            })\n\n        # ── 完税证明 ─────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67648072\":\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"wszm\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-79797899\":\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": 3, \"wszmUrl\": \"https://mock.example.com/wszm.pdf\"},\n            })\n\n        # ── 兜底 ─────────────────────\n        else:\n            print(f\"[MOCK] ⚠️ 未匹配的路径: {path}\")\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {},\n                \"message\": f\"mock: unmatched path {path}\",\n            })\n\n    def do_GET(self):\n        self.do_POST()\n\n    def log_message(self, format, *args):\n        pass  # 静默 HTTP 日志，用自己的 print\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    port = 18800\n    server = HTTPServer((\"127.0.0.1\", port), MockHandler)\n    print(f\"🧪 企享云 Mock Server 已启动: http://localhost:{port}\")\n    print(f\"   模拟所有接口，任务直接返回成功\")\n    print(f\"   Ctrl+C 停止\")\n    print()\n    try:\n        server.serve_forever()\n    except KeyboardInterrupt:\n        print(\"\\n🛑 Mock Server 已停止\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":32,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nmock_server.py — 企享云 API 模拟服务器（本地测试用）\n\n模拟所有企享云接口的返回，让你在不调真实税务局的情况下跑通整个流程。\n启动: python3 mock_server.py\n地址: http://localhost:18800\n\n测试时把 config.json 的 base_url 改成 http://localhost:18800 即可。\n\"\"\"\n\nimport json\nimport time\nimport random\nimport string\nfrom http.server import HTTPServer, BaseHTTPRequestHandler\n\n\ndef gen_task_id():\n    return str(random.randint(100000000000, 999999999999))\n\ndef gen_req_id():\n    return ''.join(random.choices(string.hexdigits.lower(), k=32))\n\n# 存储已发起的任务（task_id → 状态）\nTASKS = {}\n\n\nclass MockHandler(BaseHTTPRequestHandler):\n\n    def _read_body(self) -> dict:\n        length = int(self.headers.get(\"Content-Length\", 0))\n        if length:\n            return json.loads(self.rfile.read(length))\n        return {}\n\n    def _respond(self, data: dict, status=200):\n        body = json.dumps(data, ensure_ascii=False).encode()\n        self.send_response(status)\n        self.send_header(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json\")\n        self.send_header(\"Content-Length\", str(len(body)))\n        self.end_headers()\n        self.wfile.write(body)\n\n    def do_POST(self):\n        path = self.path.split(\"?\")[0]\n        body = self._read_body()\n        agg = body.get(\"aggOrgId\", \"mock_org\")\n\n        print(f\"[MOCK] POST {path}  body_keys={list(body.keys())}\")\n\n        # ── 鉴权 ────────────────────────\n        if path == \"/api-66569900\":\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"2000\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"token\": \"mock_token_for_testing\", \"expiresIn\": 1296000},\n            })\n\n        # ── 登录相关 ────────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-164618489\":  # check_quick_login\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"2000\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"canQuickLogin\": True},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-164576229\":  # login_tax_bureau\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"2000\", \"success\": True,\n                \"message\": \"登录成功\",\n            })\n\n        # ── 获取申报清册 ────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-66960663\":  # initiate_roster_entry\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"roster\"}  # 直接完成\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        # ── 初始化 ──────────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-69420373\":  # load_init_data_task\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"init\", \"yzpzzlDm\": body.get(\"yzpzzlDm\")}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-69497719\":  # get_init_data\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\n                    \"yzpzzlDm\": body.get(\"yzpzzlDm\", \"BDA0610606\"),\n                    \"period\": body.get(\"period\"),\n                    \"year\": body.get(\"year\"),\n                    \"initFields\": {\n                        \"sales_amount\": 0,\n                        \"output_tax\": 0,\n                        \"input_tax\": 0,\n                    },\n                    \"form_schema\": {\"fields\": [\"sales_amount\", \"exempt_sales\", \"tax_rate\"]},\n                },\n            })\n\n        # ── 上传申报 ───────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67298736\":  # upload_tax_report\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"declare\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        # ── 查询申报结果 ───────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67919304\":  # query_tax_report_result\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\n                    \"business_status\": 3,\n                    \"declareResult\": \"申报成功\",\n                    \"skje\": \"0.00\",\n                },\n            })\n\n        # ── 简易申报 ───────────────────\n        elif \"/loadSimplifiedDeclareTask\" in path:\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"simplified\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif \"/querySimplifiedDeclareTaskInfo\" in path:\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": 3, \"result\": \"申报成功\"},\n            })\n\n        # ── 财报 ───────────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67585521\":  # upload_financial_report\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"financial\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-67922325\":  # query_financial_report_result\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": 3, \"result\": \"财报申报成功\"},\n            })\n\n        # ── 轮询任务状态（核心） ────────\n        elif \"/queryTaskInfo\" in path:\n            tid = str(body.get(\"taskId\", \"\"))\n            task = TASKS.get(tid, {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"unknown\"})\n\n            result_data = {\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": task[\"status\"], \"taskId\": tid},\n            }\n\n            # 根据任务类型附加数据\n            if task[\"type\"] == \"roster\":\n                result_data[\"data\"][\"rosterEntries\"] = [\n                    {\n                        \"yzpzzlDm\": \"BDA0610606\",\n                        \"zsxmMc\": \"增值税及附加税费（小规模纳税人）\",\n                        \"tax_code\": \"VAT\",\n                        \"declareStatus\": \"未申报\",\n                        \"ssqQ\": \"2026-02-01\",\n                        \"ssqZ\": \"2026-02-28\",\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"yzpzzlDm\": \"BDA0610100\",\n                        \"zsxmMc\": \"企业所得税（季报）\",\n                        \"tax_code\": \"CIT\",\n                        \"declareStatus\": \"未申报\",\n                        \"ssqQ\": \"2026-01-01\",\n                        \"ssqZ\": \"2026-03-31\",\n                    },\n                ]\n\n            self._respond(result_data)\n\n        # ── PDF 下载 ──────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67645165\":  # load_pdf_task\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"pdf\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-212658227\":  # query_pdf_result\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\n                    \"business_status\": 3,\n                    \"pdfUrl\": \"https://mock.example.com/receipt.pdf\",\n                    \"structured_data\": {\n                        \"company_name\": \"模拟测试公司\",\n                        \"period\": \"2026-02\",\n                        \"total_tax\": \"0.00\",\n                        \"status\": \"申报成功\",\n                    },\n                },\n            })\n\n        # ── 缴款 ─────────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67662292\":  # load_payment_task\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"payment\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-67976986\":  # query_payment_result\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": 3, \"result\": \"缴款成功\"},\n            })\n\n        # ── 申报信息查询 ──────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-66965100\":  # load_declare_info_task\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"info\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        # ── 漏报检查 ─────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-66968884\":\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"missing_check\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid, \"hasMissing\": False},\n            })\n\n        # ── 完税证明 ─────────────────\n        elif path == \"/api-67648072\":\n            tid = gen_task_id()\n            TASKS[tid] = {\"status\": 3, \"type\": \"wszm\"}\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"taskId\": tid},\n            })\n\n        elif path == \"/api-79797899\":\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"business_status\": 3, \"wszmUrl\": \"https://mock.example.com/wszm.pdf\"},\n            })\n\n        # ── 兜底 ─────────────────────\n        else:\n            print(f\"[MOCK] ⚠️ 未匹配的路径: {path}\")\n            self._respond({\n                \"reqId\": gen_req_id(), \"code\": \"SUCCESS\", \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {},\n                \"message\": f\"mock: unmatched path {path}\",\n            })\n\n    def do_GET(self):\n        self.do_POST()\n\n    def log_message(self, format, *args):\n        pass  # 静默 HTTP 日志，用自己的 print\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    port = 18800\n    server = HTTPServer((\"127.0.0.1\", port), MockHandler)\n    print(f\"🧪 企享云 Mock Server 已启动: http://localhost:{port}\")\n    print(f\"   模拟所有接口，任务直接返回成功\")\n    print(f\"   Ctrl+C 停止\")\n    print()\n    try:\n        server.serve_forever()\n    except KeyboardInterrupt:\n        print(\"\\n🛑 Mock Server 已停止\")","cwd":"/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/workspace-qxy-declare"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773827707572}}
{"type":"message","id":"0169aa55","parentId":"418829c9","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:55:20.926Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the mock server API. Let me execute the tax declaration flow:\n\n1. Get token (already have: mock-token-123)\n2. Login to tax bureau\n3. Get declaration roster\n4. For each item: load init data → upload tax report → query result\n5. Financial report\n6. Missing check\n\nThe roster shows 2 items:\n- BDA0610606: 增值税及附加税费（小规模纳税人）- 2026-02\n- BDA0610100: 企业所得税（季报）- Q1 2026\n\nThe init data returns all zeros. I should NOT decide zero declaration on my own - I need to ask the user. But wait, the init fields show sales_amount=0, output_tax=0, input_tax=0. I need to confirm with the user before submitting.\n\nLet me first go through the flow up to the point where I have the data to present to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我明白了。让我来执行申报流程。首先，我需要获取申报清册并初始化数据，然后再向用户确认。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d4118429d6cb40849e65a979","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Step 1: Authenticate\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:18800/api-66569900 \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{}' | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null || curl -s -X POST http://localhost:18800/api-66569900 -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{}'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":3904,"output":530,"cacheRead":16151,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20585,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773827707578}}
